WEBVTT

1
00:37:16.510 --> 00:37:18.030 
表面上是高卢人
Gallic on the surface.

2
00:37:18.190 --> 00:37:19.750 
内里也是高卢人
Gallic to the core.

3
00:37:20.640 --> 00:37:22.920 
但是外交部有不少人开玩笑说
But there were many in the foreign office who joked that

4
00:37:22.920 --> 00:37:26.000 
康邦先生也代表俄国
Monsieur Cambon was representing Russia too.

5
00:37:26.250 --> 00:37:30.130 
因为1892年  最不可能的事情发生了
For in 1892 the impossible had happened.

6
00:37:30.390 --> 00:37:31.900 
法兰西共和国
Republican France,

7
00:37:31.900 --> 00:37:35.780 
革命的故乡  却和专制暴政的代表沙皇俄国
home to the Revolution, had signed a treaty with Tsarist Russia,

8
00:37:35.780 --> 00:37:38.030 
签署了结盟条约
the symbol of despotic tyranny.

9
00:37:38.160 --> 00:37:39.710 
他们为什么这么做
Why had they done this?

10
00:37:40.120 --> 00:37:41.390 
恐惧
Fear!

11
00:37:41.550 --> 00:37:45.510 
他们恐惧德国铁骑会再次击溃他们
Fear that they might be overwhelmed again by the German army.

12
00:37:45.880 --> 00:37:47.960 
外交大臣现在要见你  阁下
The foreign secretary will see you now, Your Excellency.

